      <h2>Built on MultiBit Merchant</h2>

      <p>MultiBit Merchant is trading, reinvented. It is designed to minimise the amount of time you have to spend
        looking after it - most of it is fully automatic. It is intended to free you from a traditional working life and
        introduce you to a different approach.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="span9">
